### 1. 注册救助者
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "rescuer001",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "张救助",
  "phone": "13800138001",
  "role": "RESCUER"
}

### 2. 注册领养者
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "adopter001",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "李领养",
  "phone": "13800138002",
  "role": "ADOPTER"
}

### 3. 注册管理员
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin001",
  "password": "admin123",
  "realName": "系统管理员",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 4. 登录（领养者）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "adopter001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 5. 登录（管理员）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin001",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 6. 发布宠物（使用已存在的救助者）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pet/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "小狗豆豆",
  "type": "狗",
  "gender": "公",
  "age": 2,
  "description": "性格温顺，已绝育，健康良好",
  "rescuer": {
    "id": 1
  }
}
